                "fragments": [
                    "In the beginning, there was silence.",
                    "Then something moved, and the movement created vibration.",
                    "Vibration became sound. Sound became music. Music became life.",
                    "This place remembers the first note ever played."
                ]
            },
            {
                "name": "The Symphony",
                "fragments": [
                    "Maestro was the first being to understand that all existence is rhythm.",
                    "They built this place as a monument to that truth.",
